== Related Topics == * {{ill|Anthropology|de|Anthropologie|ja|人類学|zh|人类学|12=draft}}. {{ill|Cultural Anthropology|de|Kulturanthropologie|ja|文化人類学|zh|文化人类学|12=draft}}, {{ill|Social Anthropology|de|Sozialanthropologie|ja|社会人類学|zh|社会人类学|12=draft}}, {{ill|Physical Anthropology|de|Physische Anthropologie|ja|自然人類学|zh|自然人类学|12=draft}}. * {{ill|human nature|de|Menschlichkeit|ja|人間性|zh|人性|12=draft}}. * {{ill|humanitarianism|de|Humanitarismus|ja|人道|zh|人道|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Homo sapiens|de|Homo sapiens|ja|ホモサピエンス|zh|智人|12=draft}}. * {{ill|philanthropy|de|Philanthropie|ja|フィランソロピー|zh|慈善事业|12=draft}} (a term derived from “to love” + “humanity”). * {{ill|humanism|de|Humanismus|ja|ヒューマニズム|zh|人文主义|12=draft}}. * {{ill|humanism (Renaissance)|de|Humanismus|ja|人文主義|zh|人文主义|12=draft}}. * {{ill|person|de|Person|ja|人|zh|人|12=draft}}、{{ill|human|de|Mensch|ja|人間|zh|人类|12=draft}} (a term focusing on {{ill|human relationships|de|Beziehungen|ja|人間関係|zh|人际关系|lt=relationship|lt_ja=関係性|lt_de=Beziehung|lt_zh=关系|12=draft}} as used in the humanities and social sciences), {{ill|human|de|Mensch|ja|ヒト|zh|人类|12=draft}} (in biology). * {{ill|human evolution|de|Menschliche Evolution|ja|人類の進化|zh|人类进化|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Spaceship Earth|de|Raumschiff Erde|ja|宇宙船地球号|zh|宇宙飞船地球号|12=draft}}. * {{ill|cosmopolitanism|de|Kosmopolitismus|ja|コスモポリタニズム|zh|世界主义|12=draft}}, {{ill|global citizen|de|Weltbürger|ja|地球市民|zh|地球公民|12=draft}}, {{ill|Earthling|de|Erdmensch|ja|地球人|zh|地球人|12=draft}}. * {{ill|humanoid|de|Humanoid|ja|ヒューマノイド|zh|类人机器人|12=draft}}.
