nded the Paris Anthropological Society, also addressed these issues—stating that the differences between races are greater than those between animal {{ill|species|de|Art|ja|種 (分類学)|zh|种 (分类学)|lt=species|lt_ja=種 (分類学)|lt_de=Art|lt_zh=种|qq=draft|qq=draft}}<ref name="philo_sakagami" />.
