=User:Immanuelle/human evolution|qq=}}. * {{ill|Spaceship Earth|de|Raumschiff Erde|ja|宇宙船地球号|zh|宇宙飞船地球号|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Spaceship Earth|qq=}}. * {{ill|cosmopolitanism|de|Kosmopolitismus|ja|コスモポリタニズム|zh|世界主义|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/cosmopolitanism|qq=}}, {{ill|global citizen|de|Weltbürger|ja|地球市民|zh|地球公民|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/global citizen|qq=}}, {{ill|Earthling|de|Erdmensch|ja|地球人|zh|地球人|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthling|qq=}}. * {{ill|humanoid|de|Humanoid|ja|ヒューマノイド|zh|类人机器人|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/humanoid|qq=}}.
